Mirae Asset Global Investments (USA) LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 5:33 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Mirae Asset Global Investments (USA) LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mirae Asset Global Investments (USA) LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment trusts. It also caters to investment companies and other investment advisers. The firm manages seperate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also launches and manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs a bottom-up approach to make its investments. The firm was founded in 2008 and is based in New York City. Mirae Asset Global Investments (USA) LLC operates as a subsidiary of Mirae Asset Global Investments (USA) Inc.


625 Madison Avenue3rd FloorNew York, NY 10022United States



Phone: 212-205-8300

Fax: 212-205-8390

investments.miraeasset.us/index.html







