 Mirae Asset Wealth Management (USA) | Wealth Management












HomeAbout UsChairman's GreetingOur Corporate History Corporate Citizenship Strong Ethical ManagementWealth ManagementValues and PhilosophyOur ProcessContact UsChairman's GreetingOur Corporate HistoryCorporate CitizenshipStrong Ethical ManagementValues and PhilosophyOur Process 


Home / Wealth Management

Wealth Management
Mirae Asset Wealth Management (USA) Inc. is a Registered Investment Advisor registered in California and New York firm serving high net worth individuals and families.  As an investment advisor, we operate our business on a fiduciary model, which simply means, our clients' interests always come first. 
With the global research capabilities of one of Asia's leading asset management firms, we are able to deliver high quality, customized portfolios through an open architecture platform.  Mirae Asset Wealth Management is dedicated to providing innovative solutions in traditional equity and fixed income, and alternative strategies such as real estate, private equity and hedge funds. 
We aim to wed our extensive experience investing in Asia and emerging markets with the experience of our U.S. advisory team. As always, we will be guided by our steadfast commitment to risk management and compliance.


Mirae Asset Wealth Management (USA)555 South Flower Street, Suite 4410Los Angeles, California 90071Telephone: 		213-262-3800Fax: 			213-262-3810Email: 			info@miraeassetusa.comWe are located in the heart of downtownLos Angeles where economic growth andglobal expansion continue to unfold.Contact Us








